* Giant Leech: Level 3–6 (by HD). Blood drain and possible disease.
* Lizard Man: Level 4–5 Humanoid.
* Werewolf (Lycanthrope): Level 6–7. Surprise on 1-3.
* Merchant: Level 2–4 Human Expert, usually with 2–8 guards (Level 3–5 Fighters).
